messages.message: Kathy’s model change (I believe this PR (https://github.com/instabase/instabase/pull/41346/files#diff-5e91ebedac6c951436fd297f78dbb961b1f4417117131be17352bb6d229396bc)) was just for field suggestions. Extraction has been using gpt-3.5-turbo for some time I believe (maybe since the beginning). I don’t think we should switch models this close to launch, unless we can be very very confident in the performance
agree, switching to davinci would affect too many things including pricing policy
